  "slug": "tapping-for-diet-guilt",
  "title": "Tapping for Diet Guilt",
  "subtitle": "An EFT sequence for the guilt that follows eating outside the rules",
  "excerpt": "An EFT tapping practice for the guilt that arrives after eating something outside whatever rules are currently in force. Works through the self-blame pattern, the all-or-nothing thinking, and the emotional cost of treating food as a moral category.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Written for homemade.education. EFT framework developed by Gary Craig (mid-1990s).",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute EFT tapping practice for diet guilt. The script works through the self-blame that follows eating outside the rules, the all-or-nothing spiral it triggers, and the emotional cost of treating food choices as moral verdicts.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "how tapping works",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/how-tapping-works"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Karate chop",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Tap the karate chop point and say each statement once:",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though I feel guilty about what I just ate and the voice telling me I've ruined everything is loud, I deeply and completely accept myself.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though I keep doing this and then hating myself for it, I am open to treating myself with some kindness anyway.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though food has become something I judge myself by, I accept myself right here, in this moment.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Tapping round",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Tap each point seven times while saying the phrase:",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Eyebrow: ",
                    "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "The guilt that arrived before the meal was even finished."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Side of eye: ",
                    "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "The voice saying I've blown it, I may as well continue."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Under eye: ",
                    "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Food as a test I keep failing."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Under nose: ",
                    "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "The cycle: restrict, lapse, shame, repeat."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Chin: ",
                    "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "How much mental space this has taken over the years."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Collarbone: ",
                    "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Treating myself as a problem to be managed through food."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Under arm: ",
                    "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "The exhaustion of this relationship with eating."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Top of head: ",
                    "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "What food has been asked to carry that isn't really about food."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Reframe to positive",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Eyebrow: ",
                    "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "One meal is one meal. It has not undone anything."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Side of eye: ",
                    "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I can choose what the next meal looks like. That is always available."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Under eye: ",
                    "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Food does not make me a good or bad person."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Under nose: ",
                    "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "The guilt is not useful information. I can put it down."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Chin: ",
                    "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "My body deserves to be fed without punishment attached."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Collarbone: ",
                    "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I am allowed to eat and not spiral."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Under arm: ",
                    "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "A calmer relationship with food is possible. I am working toward it."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Top of head: ",
                    "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I release this guilt. It has served no purpose here."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Tap each round three times, then move to the reframe and tap that three times.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where this practice comes from",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Written for homemade.education. The EFT framework is Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique, in use since the mid-1990s.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
